survey_response.review_text: So here it goes... Dr Ajay Aggarwal is a humble and quite soft spoken doctor. Quite caring. Answers each and every question to the point without beating around tge bush. Minimum tests prescribed with minimum medicines. Now that depends on the health issue. Highly recommended. I visited for chest pain, breathlessness and anxiety. And it was my second visit to the doctor within 2 months. Amazing doctor. Half of your problems would be solved by his soft spoken words. Good diagnosis too. Thank You Doctor. Regards Ishani

The experience was good in their clinic.
Doctor listened to all the queries with patience and then performed Echocardiography and 2D Echocardiography and just found out that there wasn't any problem it may be just because of Daily lifestyle or acidity

Yesterday i visited to Ajay Aggarwal for Heart Pain check-up and he suggested me not to worry more but to take medicine recommended by him.  I found charismatic personality in him and the way he suggests would be helpful. 

Thank you Practo for listed such a qualified doctor onboard.

review_reply.reply_text: There must be some reason why a particular medicine was continued which only a specialist can understand.Rather than doing doctor shopping, one should have faith in one doctor and not do self analysis of medicines and treatments, rather reconsult if facing any issues...Managing patients and queue is also the job of owner of clinic but it does not mean that patient care is neglected,each patient poor or rich is important to us...thanks

survey_response.review_text:
Visited Dr. Ajay seeing practo reviews. But all its true in this case. Dr. Ajay is lost in looking for patient queue and how many patients were there. We visited today and were the first one and the doctor completely engrossed in his own thoughts. Didn't pay any attention and prescribe *** ****** medicine. We told the first one prescribed didn't help in reduction of BP but he was little concerned about it.
Not at all a good clinic I would say
Would never recommend anyone.

He is a great  doctor  , he listens  patiently to each n every suffering of a patient.   He will suggest  only necessary  test and prescribed  medication.  His consultation  charges are also nominal  in comparison  to other cardiologists in north west  Delhi.  I'll definitely  recommend  this doctor for any cardiac problem. 
 Regards 
mansi uppal
